From 32c66374b1474bd8defbcee954880ec788ff6e06 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Fri, 24 Jul 2026 14:21:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove resume and add 3D GitHub project visuals

Drop resume CTAs/PDF, curate featured repos with richer copy, and render live R3F motifs on project cards so the projects section is visual instead of plain text.
---
 README.md                          |   5 +-
 public/resume.pdf                  | Bin 341884 -> 0 bytes
 src/app/globals.css                |  26 ++
 src/components/ContactSection.tsx  |   4 +-
 src/components/Hero.tsx            |   8 +-
 src/components/ProjectScene.tsx    | 435 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/components/ProjectsSection.tsx | 254 ++++++++++++++---
 src/lib/github.ts                  |   8 +-
 src/lib/site-config.ts             |  86 +++++-
 9 files changed, 776 insertions(+), 50 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 public/resume.pdf
 create mode 100644 src/components/ProjectScene.tsx

diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
index b6fc56a..ed2f735 100644
--- a/README.md
+++ b/README.md
@@ -7,6 +7,7 @@ A dark, cinematic portfolio inspired by [Ricardo Chance](https://ricardochance.c
 - Full-screen hero with interactive 3D particle star (mouse-responsive)
 - Minimal navigation with corner frame accents
 - About, GitHub Projects, Blog, and Contact sections
+- Featured GitHub projects with live 3D React Three Fiber visuals
 - GitHub repos fetched from the API (revalidated hourly)
 - Fully responsive layout
 - Vercel-ready deployment
@@ -22,9 +23,7 @@ Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000).
 
 ## Customize
 
-Edit `src/lib/site-config.ts` for your name, copy, email, and social links.
-
-Replace `public/resume.pdf` with your actual resume PDF.
+Edit `src/lib/site-config.ts` for your name, copy, email, social links, and featured project list.
 
 ## Environment Variables
 
diff --git a/public/resume.pdf b/public/resume.pdf
